column1: ### LEGEND
## SCAFF in SafAle: Scaffold ID in the SafAle denovo assembly
## POS: Position on SCAFF
## REF: Consensus character state in the SafAle denovo assembly (inherited from the VCF file)
## ALT: Additional character states in 404 based on BWA output (inherited from the VCF file)
## DP: Coverage (inherited from the VCF file)
## TYPE: Variant type, snp or complex (inherited from the VCF file)
## 424 is Heterozygote: Descendant is Heterozygote - True or False
## SefAle is Heterozygote: Ancestor is Heterozygote - True or False
## 424 states: Infered from VCF resulting from mapping Descendant reads to SefAle genome
## SefAle states: Infered from VCF resulting from mapping SefAle reads to SefAle genome
## Gene Name: Inherited from eggNOG orthologs or SGD
## Comment:
# LOH: Loss of heterozygocity through deletion or through homologous/non-hologous recombination
# GOH: Gain of heterozygocity through point mutation
# Complex mutation: Indel of one or more bases
# No-gene LOH: Loss of heterozygocity outside detected genes
# No-gene GOH: Gain of heterozygocity outside detected genes
# No-gene: SNP outside detected genes, zygocity retained
# Intron LOH: Loss of heterozygocity in intron
# Intron GOH: Gain of heterozygocity in intron
# Intron: SNP in intron, zygocity retained
# Codon contains ambiguity symbol: Inference avoided due to uncertainty
# Point nutation Non-synonymous, homozygous to homozygous
# Point nutation Synonymous, homozygous to homozygous
# Retained heterozygocity

## SCAFF in SafAle: Scaffold ID in the SafAle denovo assembly
## POS: Position on SCAFF
## REF: Consensus character state in the SafAle denovo assembly (inherited from the VCF file)
## ALT: Additional character states in 404 based on BWA output (inherited from the VCF file)
## DP: Coverage (inherited from the VCF file)
## TYPE: Variant type, snp or complex (inherited from the VCF file)
## 424 is Heterozygote: Descendant is Heterozygote - True or False
## SefAle is Heterozygote: Ancestor is Heterozygote - True or False
## 424 states: Infered from VCF resulting from mapping Descendant reads to SefAle genome
## SefAle states: Infered from VCF resulting from mapping SefAle reads to SefAle genome
## Gene Name: Inherited from eggNOG orthologs or SGD
## Comment:
# LOH: Loss of heterozygosity through deletion or through homologous/non-hologous recombination
# GOH: Gain of heterozygosity through point mutation
# Complex mutation: Indel of one or more bases
# No-gene LOH: Loss of heterozygosity outside detected genes
# No-gene GOH: Gain of heterozygosity outside detected genes
# No-gene: SNP outside detected genes, zygocity retained
# Intron LOH: Loss of heterozygosity in intron
# Intron GOH: Gain of heterozygosity in intron
# Intron: SNP in intron, zygocity retained
# Codon contains ambiguity symbol: Inference avoided due to uncertainty
